<view class="page">
  <view class="material-head">
    <text class="eyebrow">材料</text>
    <view class="title">把证据整理清楚</view>
    <view class="muted copy">每份材料都会标记用途和状态，补齐后再生成测算会更稳。</view>
  </view>

  <view wx:for="{{materials}}" wx:key="group" class="group">
    <view class="section-title group-title">{{item.group}}</view>
    <view
      wx:for="{{item.items}}"
      wx:for-item="material"
      wx:key="name"
      class="card material-card"
    >
      <view class="material-info">
        <view class="material-name">{{material.name}}</view>
        <view class="muted purpose">{{material.purpose}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="material-side">
        <text class="pill {{material.status === '已通过' ? 'risk-low' : material.status === '需补充' ? 'risk-mid' : material.status === '未上传' ? '' : 'risk-high'}}">
          {{material.status}}
        </text>
        <button class="upload-button" data-name="{{material.name}}" bindtap="upload">
          {{material.status === '已通过' ? '查看' : material.status === '需补充' ? '补充' : '上传'}}
        </button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="danger-panel">
    上传病历、身份证、收入证明等敏感材料前，正式版本会再次征得单独授权。
  </view>
</view>
